freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Digestive issues.  Diarrhea for a day.  Never had diarrhea like this, it was like very diluted sand.
My joints are aching like that they did the day after my second vaccination and I am also more fatigued.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: The only thing I have noticed is a sluggish feeling each evening sometimes feeling like Im going to come down with something but I always feel good in the am.
